body:
So after some thinking I’m putting some of these fae species up for sale. They are called Pudmos.


1: $10

2: $10

3: $10

4: $10

5: $15

6: $15


(PayPal only)

You will get the single file and a better quality png.


A fae species native to my own world, they are uber colorful and can come in many many varieties, some are more colorful then others. They have two sets of hands, one is for shoveling dirt/ground/rocks while the other is for grasping and tearing. Usually depending on their preferred fruit, they can take colors from that. Their blood is sweet and can be eaten but they have a big bite and will chomp if attacked.

They live in tropical ponds or warmer waters, usually building/residing in coral reefs. They are Omnivores but prefer fruit and bug based diet instead of meat.

-These guys are still being worked out so bear with me! Art and species by me

summary:
Goretober day 2: Cyborg 
"She's not even HUMAN" Emri was a leader in the Cyborg uprising but was captured by human government...
body:
Goretober day 2: Cyborg

“She’s not even HUMAN” Emri was a leader in the Cyborg uprising but was captured by human government officials. She was sentenced to death and as an added punishment, her execution was made public. To further humiliate her, her clothes were stripped away and she was forced upon her knees. Her blood is black due to it being made of oil. (thanks @kyotehwarlord for the suggestion)•

Commissions are open! Just dm me!

•
